Just so everyone knows, many of the bases could have picked up the energy 
released by the Violator warping in. However no bases or charachters can 
Detect the Violator because it possess stealth, which renders it invisible to 
all scanners and such. Meaning Energy Signature seeking weapons or any kind 
of seeking weapons will not be able to lock onto it.

--part1_df.15997d6b.284adde6_boundary
